  "2026-07-14T08:05:12.058Z",claude-opus,"Fixed: extractRelationships now dedups by (from,to,kind). Verified: brief blockers shows single blocked_by edge (was doubled on 2026.7.12); 45/45 unit tests incl. new dedup regression test."
